@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-card">
        <h1 class="legal-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="legal-lead">
            Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.
        </p>

        <hr class="legal-divider"/>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our website, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal details such as name and email address when you register or make a booking</li>
            <li>Booking and reservation details related to travel packages</li>
            <li>Communication data when you contact us or join a waiting list</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To manage bookings, reservations, and waiting lists</li>
            <li>To communicate with you regarding your account, bookings, or availability updates</li>
            <li>To improve our services and user experience</li>
            <li>To ensure the security and proper functioning of the website</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Protection</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</p>

        <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. Your data may only be shared when required by law or when necessary to provide our services.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to manage user sessions and improve functionality. By using our website, you agree to the use of cookies.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, or request deletion of your personal information. If you have any questions or requests regarding your data, please contact us.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be published on this page.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the website.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    /* Page background */
    .legal-page {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
        padding: 40px 16px 70px;
        background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 20% 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.10), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 100% 10%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.10), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    /* Card */
    .legal-card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 920px;
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.08);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 28px 26px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.10), 0 4px 10px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.06);
    }

    /* Typography */
    .legal-title {
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #0f172a;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    .legal-lead {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #475569;
        margin: 0 0 18px;
    }

    .legal-card h2 {
        margin: 22px 0 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #0f172a;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 12px;
    }

    .legal-card h2::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 4px;
        width: 4px;
        height: 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .legal-card p {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: #334155;
    }

    /* Divider */
    .legal-divider {
        margin: 18px 0 6px;
        border: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #cbd5e1, transparent);
    }

    /* Lists */
    .legal-card ul {
        margin: 10px 0 16px;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .legal-card li {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .legal-card li::before {
        content: "✓";
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #2563eb;
        margin-top: 1px;
    }

    /* Links (if you add later) */
    .legal-card a {
        color: #2563eb;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .legal-card a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .legal-title {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .legal-card h2 {
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .legal-card p, .legal-card li {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
       
</style>